AlcesActsAsFolder
==============

This add all the common functions for a dependent model which acts a folder.

class.visible(*args)
class.visible(:all)
class.visible(:first)
class.visible(:id)

instance.folder
instance.folder(name)

call back function for create/update/delete to make sure the folder names are in sync and that folder is created.


Example
=======

acts_as_folder :root

The root is generally a project or another folder as expects. This creates a belongs_to relationship
and expects to find a folder(name) in the other model.


